                                <p>Supports backup and disaster recovery solutions through CloudStack’s <strong>APIs and extensible architecture</strong>, enabling third-party tools and services to seamlessly integrate with the platform for data protection and continuity.</p>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col">
