                                <h2 class="integration-title"><img src="Integrations2_files/containers_icon.svg" alt="" class="me-3">Containers</h2>
                                <p>CloudStack supports different 
containers through its Container Service, which can manage and 
orchestrate container-based workloads alongside traditional virtual 
machines, <strong>providing a unified cloud infrastructure platform</strong>.</p>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col">
                                        <div class="tab-box box-kubernetes box192"><img src="Integrations2_files/kubernetes_logo.svg" alt=""></div>
